headline.print_headline: Ogier Takes Overall Lead With Mexico Win
headline.main: Ogier Takes Overall Lead With Mexico Win

lead_paragraph: World rally champion Sebastien Ogier took the lead in the overall standings on Sunday after winning the Rally of Mexico ahead of Volkswagen team mate Jari-Matti Latvala.
